init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was like, "I'm going to have to go back to the drawing board on this one."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf went back to the woods and he was like, "I'm going to have to think of a new plan."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He had his teeth, he had his claws, he had his fangs, he had his tail, he had his paws, he had his nose

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf thought about the little pig's house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was made out of depleted uranium.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf thought about this for a while and then he got an idea.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the wolf went to the uranium mine and he got a bunch of uranium ore and he took it to the blacksmith and he said,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf went to the little pig's house and he started sawing and sawing and sawing and sawing and sawing and sawing and

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf was like, "I'm going to have to think of something else."
